PRE-REQS
================================================================================
This project is built using gradle.  Currently version 0.8 is being used.
Go to http://www.gradle.org and download gradle-0.8-all.zip.  Unzip gradle
wherever you like, but make sure it's on your PATH. 

BUILDING
================================================================================
Usage of gradle is very similar to ant.  Simply cd to the project directory and
execute gradle compile.

NOTE: You can see the list of tasks available via gradle -t

GENERATING ECLIPSE PROJECT
================================================================================
Execute gradle eclipse and a new eclipse project will be created with all of
the needed libraries.

